dc_description_s: Ancillary map: Fès el Bali -- Fès Jdid. Scale 1:5,000. "Autorisation no 313 du 6 Mars 1979 - Division de la cartographie - Rabat." Accompanying text: Faillard, René. Plan-guide de Fès : répertoire, quartiers, avenues, boulevards, rues, places, rond-points. Accompanying text includes indices, photographs, advertisements, and general information. "Société nouvelle des impressions et cartonnages idéale." Includes index to points of interest.
